WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.243 align:middle line:90%


00:00:01.243 --> 00:00:02.660 align:middle line:84%
>> Hello, I'm
Georgia Shakti-Hill.

00:00:02.660 --> 00:00:05.460 align:middle line:84%
And I am so pleased to bring
one of the friends of "Living

00:00:05.460 --> 00:00:08.370 align:middle line:84%
in Balance" back and
author Angela Trafford.

00:00:08.370 --> 00:00:10.890 align:middle line:84%
She has new wisdom and
new light to share.

00:00:10.890 --> 00:00:13.200 align:middle line:84%
Come join us "Living in
Balance on Shakti-Hill."

00:00:13.200 --> 00:00:16.434 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:00:16.434 --> 00:00:34.740 align:middle line:90%


00:00:34.740 --> 00:00:36.360 align:middle line:84%
"Remembering the
Language of God:

00:00:36.360 --> 00:00:38.400 align:middle line:84%
The Forgotten Path,"
that is the title,

00:00:38.400 --> 00:00:41.730 align:middle line:84%
and the author we have with us,
Angela Trafford, and welcome.

00:00:41.730 --> 00:00:43.017 align:middle line:90%
>> Thank you so much, Georgia.

00:00:43.017 --> 00:00:44.100 align:middle line:90%
Thank you for inviting me.

00:00:44.100 --> 00:00:44.900 align:middle line:90%
>> Ah!

00:00:44.900 --> 00:00:47.730 align:middle line:84%
We have a wonderful new
book that you have just

00:00:47.730 --> 00:00:50.850 align:middle line:84%
created and published
for us, and there is much

00:00:50.850 --> 00:00:53.370 align:middle line:84%
that you have learned
since the first book

00:00:53.370 --> 00:00:54.660 align:middle line:90%
that you wrote for us before.

00:00:54.660 --> 00:00:56.170 align:middle line:90%
>> That's so true.

00:00:56.170 --> 00:00:58.230 align:middle line:84%
And being a student
of life, I am learning

00:00:58.230 --> 00:00:59.910 align:middle line:90%
every moment of each day.

00:00:59.910 --> 00:01:01.800 align:middle line:84%
>> And you were on
our program before,

00:01:01.800 --> 00:01:04.170 align:middle line:84%
and we called it "Miracles
and Self-Healing."

00:01:04.170 --> 00:01:06.760 align:middle line:84%
And so the healing process
is continuing for Angela?

00:01:06.760 --> 00:01:09.885 align:middle line:84%
>> Yes, and living in the
land of the miraculous.

00:01:09.885 --> 00:01:11.640 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHTER]

00:01:11.640 --> 00:01:12.980 align:middle line:90%
Something new happens every day.

00:01:12.980 --> 00:01:13.780 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes.

00:01:13.780 --> 00:01:16.680 align:middle line:84%
Well, OK, now let's just
look at this new book,

00:01:16.680 --> 00:01:18.650 align:middle line:84%
"Remembering the
Language of God."

00:01:18.650 --> 00:01:21.120 align:middle line:90%
OK, what is the language of God?

00:01:21.120 --> 00:01:24.810 align:middle line:84%
>> The language of God and the
title "Remembering the Language

00:01:24.810 --> 00:01:30.000 align:middle line:84%
of God" simply is stating
that each of us is born with

00:01:30.000 --> 00:01:36.150 align:middle line:84%
a primordial gift of the
divine within ourselves,

00:01:36.150 --> 00:01:41.340 align:middle line:84%
and we lose the connection to
that gift through childhood

00:01:41.340 --> 00:01:46.170 align:middle line:84%
and the experiences of the lack
of unconditional love and even

00:01:46.170 --> 00:01:48.480 align:middle line:90%
abuse in our childhood.

00:01:48.480 --> 00:01:51.030 align:middle line:84%
And then as we
grow up, we attract

00:01:51.030 --> 00:01:53.110 align:middle line:90%
destructive relationships.

00:01:53.110 --> 00:01:55.290 align:middle line:84%
And so each of us
reaches a point

00:01:55.290 --> 00:01:59.700 align:middle line:84%
in our life where the suffering
is so intense that we've

00:01:59.700 --> 00:02:02.940 align:middle line:84%
attracted crisis in our
life, and that is the time

00:02:02.940 --> 00:02:09.270 align:middle line:84%
to go within, and we can act
and feel the pain of our lives

00:02:09.270 --> 00:02:12.480 align:middle line:84%
because only through
reconnecting with that pain

00:02:12.480 --> 00:02:15.510 align:middle line:84%
and feeling the feelings
can we connect with God

00:02:15.510 --> 00:02:17.610 align:middle line:90%
as human beings on this earth.

00:02:17.610 --> 00:02:20.880 align:middle line:84%
>> So it's, really, each person
comes to their moment of truth

00:02:20.880 --> 00:02:25.320 align:middle line:84%
when they're forced to look
again at their own divineness

00:02:25.320 --> 00:02:27.850 align:middle line:84%
because it's too harsh
out there in reality?

00:02:27.850 --> 00:02:28.650 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHS]

00:02:28.650 --> 00:02:31.650 align:middle line:84%
>> Exactly, because
their life experience

00:02:31.650 --> 00:02:35.850 align:middle line:84%
and the destructiveness of their
relationships has not brought

00:02:35.850 --> 00:02:39.970 align:middle line:84%
them the fulfillment and the
happiness that they expected.

00:02:39.970 --> 00:02:42.510 align:middle line:84%
And so we had to expand
ourselves in order

00:02:42.510 --> 00:02:45.810 align:middle line:84%
to embrace another
point of view,

00:02:45.810 --> 00:02:49.380 align:middle line:84%
and transform ourselves-- first,
with the conditioning of what

00:02:49.380 --> 00:02:52.260 align:middle line:84%
we've been taught, and
then opening the heart

00:02:52.260 --> 00:02:54.960 align:middle line:84%
and feeling the pain
that will lead us

00:02:54.960 --> 00:02:58.620 align:middle line:90%
into the language of God.

00:02:58.620 --> 00:03:00.800 align:middle line:84%
>> And the subtitle is
"The Forgotten Path."

00:03:00.800 --> 00:03:03.360 align:middle line:90%
So we forgot our divineness.

00:03:03.360 --> 00:03:07.710 align:middle line:84%
We forgot that essence of the
bubbly, blissful, childlike

00:03:07.710 --> 00:03:08.550 align:middle line:90%
part of our lives.

00:03:08.550 --> 00:03:12.960 align:middle line:84%
>> That's right, and we have
forgotten this because we are

00:03:12.960 --> 00:03:17.550 align:middle line:84%
living in an age of technology
and most of us have become very

00:03:17.550 --> 00:03:19.290 align:middle line:90%
intellectualized.

00:03:19.290 --> 00:03:22.530 align:middle line:84%
And therefore, we are out of
touch with our true feelings

00:03:22.530 --> 00:03:24.090 align:middle line:84%
and living life
according to what

00:03:24.090 --> 00:03:29.640 align:middle line:84%
we've been taught to believe
by our parents, by our society,

00:03:29.640 --> 00:03:31.500 align:middle line:90%
and by our churches.

00:03:31.500 --> 00:03:34.830 align:middle line:84%
And so in order to go to the
next step of our evolution,

00:03:34.830 --> 00:03:37.380 align:middle line:84%
we have to open
our hearts to what

00:03:37.380 --> 00:03:40.230 align:middle line:84%
I believe is the
experience of God that

00:03:40.230 --> 00:03:42.760 align:middle line:90%
is ongoing for each one of us.

00:03:42.760 --> 00:03:44.730 align:middle line:84%
But it's a point
in our evolution

00:03:44.730 --> 00:03:49.650 align:middle line:84%
that we have to learn how to
do this because we've lost our,

00:03:49.650 --> 00:03:52.350 align:middle line:84%
not the gift, but
we've lost the way,

00:03:52.350 --> 00:03:55.800 align:middle line:84%
and it is really the way
of love that we've lost.

00:03:55.800 --> 00:04:00.060 align:middle line:84%
And being intellectualized
in our ego, most of us

00:04:00.060 --> 00:04:01.980 align:middle line:90%
get lost in that control.

00:04:01.980 --> 00:04:04.200 align:middle line:84%
And we have to
really learn what it

00:04:04.200 --> 00:04:06.910 align:middle line:84%
means to experience
the humility,

00:04:06.910 --> 00:04:11.700 align:middle line:84%
the gratitude, the unconditional
love that is the way of love.

00:04:11.700 --> 00:04:13.830 align:middle line:10%
>> Well, as I was
reading the book,

00:04:13.830 --> 00:04:16.860 align:middle line:10%
I was feeling badly for you
because I thought, gosh,

00:04:16.860 --> 00:04:21.180 align:middle line:10%
you have created a wonderful
counseling service that you do

00:04:21.180 --> 00:04:24.100 align:middle line:10%
called self-healing,
and people come to you,

00:04:24.100 --> 00:04:25.880 align:middle line:10%
and you work with
them, you counsel them.

00:04:25.880 --> 00:04:28.920 align:middle line:10%
But people come to you when
they're in a lot of pain,

00:04:28.920 --> 00:04:30.630 align:middle line:10%
and much of what
you have learned

00:04:30.630 --> 00:04:33.810 align:middle line:10%
about these difficulties is
that people come to you when

00:04:33.810 --> 00:04:37.230 align:middle line:10%
they are in need, and you
have learned techniques

00:04:37.230 --> 00:04:40.440 align:middle line:10%
that can help them self-heal.

00:04:40.440 --> 00:04:45.060 align:middle line:84%
>> Exactly, and I feel very
fortunate that I am in that

00:04:45.060 --> 00:04:47.850 align:middle line:84%
position where people do come
to me when they're in pain

00:04:47.850 --> 00:04:51.990 align:middle line:84%
because people become very
real when they are experiencing

00:04:51.990 --> 00:04:53.230 align:middle line:90%
the pain of our lives.

00:04:53.230 --> 00:04:55.200 align:middle line:84%
And you've probably
noticed yourself

00:04:55.200 --> 00:04:59.200 align:middle line:84%
how much in illusion
people are today.

00:04:59.200 --> 00:05:01.740 align:middle line:84%
People have all
kinds of conceptions

00:05:01.740 --> 00:05:05.790 align:middle line:84%
of what spirituality is,
religious conceptions of what

00:05:05.790 --> 00:05:07.510 align:middle line:90%
god is all about.

00:05:07.510 --> 00:05:12.750 align:middle line:84%
And so when people face
mortal illness, when

00:05:12.750 --> 00:05:18.030 align:middle line:84%
they face divorce, separation,
when people fall in love, when

00:05:18.030 --> 00:05:22.230 align:middle line:84%
life comes in and
intrudes on our plans,

00:05:22.230 --> 00:05:24.900 align:middle line:84%
that's when we are
forced to open our hearts

00:05:24.900 --> 00:05:28.360 align:middle line:84%
and find out what
life is really about.

00:05:28.360 --> 00:05:31.080 align:middle line:84%
And what we find
is that it is not

00:05:31.080 --> 00:05:32.770 align:middle line:90%
what we were taught to believe.

00:05:32.770 --> 00:05:36.400 align:middle line:84%
And so then we have to find out
what is the reality of life,

00:05:36.400 --> 00:05:37.900 align:middle line:90%
and that's our challenge.

00:05:37.900 --> 00:05:41.210 align:middle line:84%
>> Does this happen to us
once or does it happen again

00:05:41.210 --> 00:05:42.010 align:middle line:90%
and again?

00:05:42.010 --> 00:05:45.820 align:middle line:84%
Is it like we wake up to a
point, and then we're OK,

00:05:45.820 --> 00:05:48.250 align:middle line:84%
or are we going to be
then challenged again

00:05:48.250 --> 00:05:49.330 align:middle line:90%
to look within?

00:05:49.330 --> 00:05:52.360 align:middle line:84%
>> Well, we are always
challenged each day.

00:05:52.360 --> 00:05:54.730 align:middle line:84%
Each choice you
make is a challenge.

00:05:54.730 --> 00:05:57.790 align:middle line:84%
But some of us are aware
of that and others aren't.

00:05:57.790 --> 00:06:00.430 align:middle line:84%
That's the difference between
being unconscious and then

00:06:00.430 --> 00:06:03.820 align:middle line:84%
becoming a conscious
human being.

00:06:03.820 --> 00:06:06.580 align:middle line:84%
So yes, we are
challenged each day.

00:06:06.580 --> 00:06:10.690 align:middle line:84%
But we don't have to
reach the point of crisis.

00:06:10.690 --> 00:06:14.710 align:middle line:84%
If we find ourselves and open
our hearts on our path in life

00:06:14.710 --> 00:06:18.220 align:middle line:84%
and truly learn how to
love first ourselves

00:06:18.220 --> 00:06:21.820 align:middle line:84%
and then how to share that love
with our fellow human beings,

00:06:21.820 --> 00:06:24.700 align:middle line:90%
that's quite, to me, the task.

00:06:24.700 --> 00:06:27.640 align:middle line:84%
The purpose of each one of us
that's born onto this planet

00:06:27.640 --> 00:06:29.210 align:middle line:90%
is to learn that.

00:06:29.210 --> 00:06:31.750 align:middle line:84%
But you can't learn
that without feeling

00:06:31.750 --> 00:06:34.760 align:middle line:90%
the pain that is part of life.

00:06:34.760 --> 00:06:40.060 align:middle line:84%
>> So our lessons that are hard,
they really then are our gifts

00:06:40.060 --> 00:06:43.930 align:middle line:84%
if we move past them, if we
don't stay in the victim mode.

00:06:43.930 --> 00:06:46.330 align:middle line:84%
We have to move out of the
victim though, don't we?

00:06:46.330 --> 00:06:47.500 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes, we do.

00:06:47.500 --> 00:06:52.750 align:middle line:84%
And we also have to learn
how to go within and feel

00:06:52.750 --> 00:06:56.860 align:middle line:84%
the emotional honesty that
allows us to [CHUCKLES]

00:06:56.860 --> 00:07:01.930 align:middle line:84%
turn some of the
experiences in our life that

00:07:01.930 --> 00:07:05.470 align:middle line:90%
would be hurtful into our good.

00:07:05.470 --> 00:07:07.930 align:middle line:84%
I always say that I've
been spinning straw

00:07:07.930 --> 00:07:12.760 align:middle line:84%
into gold for the past
13 years, and that's

00:07:12.760 --> 00:07:17.200 align:middle line:84%
the art of living as far as I'm
concerned, it's how to do that.

00:07:17.200 --> 00:07:21.910 align:middle line:84%
>> And your story for the people
who have not met you before--

00:07:21.910 --> 00:07:24.770 align:middle line:84%
the first book that you
wrote is "The Heroic Path."

00:07:24.770 --> 00:07:25.570 align:middle line:90%
>> That's right.

00:07:25.570 --> 00:07:29.380 align:middle line:84%
>> And you-- just tell us that
story because it is beautiful

00:07:29.380 --> 00:07:31.480 align:middle line:90%
of the way you healed.

00:07:31.480 --> 00:07:33.110 align:middle line:90%
>> Well, that's quite a story.

00:07:33.110 --> 00:07:33.910 align:middle line:90%
>> It is.

00:07:33.910 --> 00:07:38.680 align:middle line:84%
>> I have to try and put it
in as few words as possible.

00:07:38.680 --> 00:07:41.170 align:middle line:84%
I was living an
unconscious life,

00:07:41.170 --> 00:07:45.220 align:middle line:84%
in denial of my feelings like so
many of my brothers and sisters

00:07:45.220 --> 00:07:48.760 align:middle line:84%
until I finally crash-landed
into the reality of my life

00:07:48.760 --> 00:07:51.160 align:middle line:84%
through the
experience of cancer.

00:07:51.160 --> 00:07:52.960 align:middle line:84%
And I had to face
the fact that I

00:07:52.960 --> 00:07:56.200 align:middle line:84%
was going to die without
ever having lived.

00:07:56.200 --> 00:07:59.140 align:middle line:84%
And I decided that
I wanted to live

00:07:59.140 --> 00:08:01.930 align:middle line:84%
and that it was my
responsibility that if I wanted

00:08:01.930 --> 00:08:05.560 align:middle line:84%
to live, that I had to take
responsibility for my life

00:08:05.560 --> 00:08:08.050 align:middle line:84%
and be responsible
for the choices

00:08:08.050 --> 00:08:11.510 align:middle line:84%
that I had to make in
order to heal my life.

00:08:11.510 --> 00:08:16.090 align:middle line:84%
And I found myself going
within through prayer

00:08:16.090 --> 00:08:19.690 align:middle line:84%
and journaling and
expressing my feelings

00:08:19.690 --> 00:08:22.180 align:middle line:84%
and standing up for
myself in my life,

00:08:22.180 --> 00:08:24.220 align:middle line:90%
and that was the start of it.

00:08:24.220 --> 00:08:28.630 align:middle line:84%
And going through many,
many painful experiences

00:08:28.630 --> 00:08:30.580 align:middle line:84%
in trying to heal
of cancer and then

00:08:30.580 --> 00:08:33.760 align:middle line:84%
in losing my children
through a custody

00:08:33.760 --> 00:08:38.830 align:middle line:84%
battle with my
abusive ex-husband

00:08:38.830 --> 00:08:42.820 align:middle line:84%
forced me to surrender my life
to God and to let go of my life

00:08:42.820 --> 00:08:46.120 align:middle line:84%
to God and to ask God
to show me how to live.

00:08:46.120 --> 00:08:49.660 align:middle line:84%
>> So you were empowered that
you had to take responsibility,

00:08:49.660 --> 00:08:53.440 align:middle line:84%
you had to make choices that
took the control of your life

00:08:53.440 --> 00:08:57.580 align:middle line:84%
back so that you could be the
person that you wanted to be.

00:08:57.580 --> 00:09:01.960 align:middle line:84%
>> I had to let go and surrender
my life in order to take back

00:09:01.960 --> 00:09:02.760 align:middle line:90%
my life.

00:09:02.760 --> 00:09:03.560 align:middle line:90%
>> [LAUGHS]

00:09:03.560 --> 00:09:06.820 align:middle line:84%
>> It's like Jesus said, "He who
loses his life, shall find it."

00:09:06.820 --> 00:09:09.910 align:middle line:84%
>> And it is interesting how--
and you have to know when you

00:09:09.910 --> 00:09:13.480 align:middle line:84%
need to surrender and just let
go and let God and just go with

00:09:13.480 --> 00:09:16.640 align:middle line:84%
the flow and then when is
it time to take it back.

00:09:16.640 --> 00:09:17.440 align:middle line:90%
>> Well--

00:09:17.440 --> 00:09:18.550 align:middle line:90%
>> It takes power.

00:09:18.550 --> 00:09:20.320 align:middle line:90%
>> Desperation causes a lot of--

00:09:20.320 --> 00:09:21.580 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHTER]

00:09:21.580 --> 00:09:24.420 align:middle line:84%
>> --suffering to a
point of desperation too.

00:09:24.420 --> 00:09:27.490 align:middle line:84%
And that's what happened to me,
where I just literally caved

00:09:27.490 --> 00:09:30.490 align:middle line:84%
in and fell on my knees
in my living room floor

00:09:30.490 --> 00:09:32.410 align:middle line:90%
and surrendered my life to God.

00:09:32.410 --> 00:09:35.230 align:middle line:84%
And afterward, in
finding out that I

00:09:35.230 --> 00:09:37.570 align:middle line:84%
had lost the custody
of my children

00:09:37.570 --> 00:09:39.520 align:middle line:84%
and have the
occurrence of cancer,

00:09:39.520 --> 00:09:42.730 align:middle line:84%
I began to go within
through meditation, prayer,

00:09:42.730 --> 00:09:45.010 align:middle line:84%
and visualization
and start to get

00:09:45.010 --> 00:09:47.500 align:middle line:84%
in touch with the
reality of my life

00:09:47.500 --> 00:09:51.940 align:middle line:84%
and had an experience where
I felt a white light moving

00:09:51.940 --> 00:09:54.010 align:middle line:90%
through my body, healing me.

00:09:54.010 --> 00:09:57.700 align:middle line:84%
And in essence, God
really healed me

00:09:57.700 --> 00:10:01.160 align:middle line:84%
through a miracle in
opening to this white light.

00:10:01.160 --> 00:10:04.690 align:middle line:84%
And I had a healing which
changed my entire life

00:10:04.690 --> 00:10:08.110 align:middle line:84%
and put me on a path
of miracles where I now

00:10:08.110 --> 00:10:10.700 align:middle line:84%
recovered the custody
of my children

00:10:10.700 --> 00:10:13.690 align:middle line:84%
and have been with my children
for the past seven years

00:10:13.690 --> 00:10:15.610 align:middle line:90%
and then also--

00:10:15.610 --> 00:10:16.720 align:middle line:90%
>> Healed of cancer.

00:10:16.720 --> 00:10:22.210 align:middle line:84%
>> --healed of cancer and
got on the path of recovering

00:10:22.210 --> 00:10:26.530 align:middle line:84%
my purpose of life, which was
to start my work, self-healing,

00:10:26.530 --> 00:10:33.880 align:middle line:84%
and to teach people how to love
and that love beginning with

00:10:33.880 --> 00:10:38.290 align:middle line:84%
our own hearts for each
one of us inside ourselves,

00:10:38.290 --> 00:10:41.260 align:middle line:84%
which is what I think
we have really lost.

00:10:41.260 --> 00:10:43.650 align:middle line:84%
I mean, most of us
can love other people,

00:10:43.650 --> 00:10:47.640 align:middle line:84%
but it's hard to go
within and love yourself.

00:10:47.640 --> 00:10:49.200 align:middle line:84%
>> But that is the
beginning point.

00:10:49.200 --> 00:10:50.520 align:middle line:90%
We have to forgive ourselves.

00:10:50.520 --> 00:10:51.820 align:middle line:90%
We have to love ourselves.

00:10:51.820 --> 00:10:54.780 align:middle line:84%
And so the healing
starts with the self.

00:10:54.780 --> 00:10:57.480 align:middle line:84%
And then we are better
lovers and healers

00:10:57.480 --> 00:11:00.580 align:middle line:84%
to others if we have
gotten back to that point.

00:11:00.580 --> 00:11:01.890 align:middle line:90%
>> Well, it's the only way.

00:11:01.890 --> 00:11:04.590 align:middle line:84%
