a heroic path,

00:16:49.100 --> 00:16:52.980 align:middle line:84%
us being out of the
light of God's love.

00:16:52.980 --> 00:16:54.420 align:middle line:90%
And so what does that mean?

00:16:54.420 --> 00:16:56.000 align:middle line:90%
It means that we're in darkness.

00:16:56.000 --> 00:16:58.010 align:middle line:84%
How do you come out
of the darkness?

00:16:58.010 --> 00:16:59.810 align:middle line:90%
You have to be humble.

00:16:59.810 --> 00:17:01.850 align:middle line:90%
You have to find humility.

00:17:01.850 --> 00:17:03.800 align:middle line:90%
You have to become grateful.

00:17:03.800 --> 00:17:06.290 align:middle line:84%
And most of all, the
most important thing

00:17:06.290 --> 00:17:08.690 align:middle line:84%
is you have to get in
touch with your pain,

00:17:08.690 --> 00:17:13.579 align:middle line:84%
and not just the pain of your
life, but pain as part of life

00:17:13.579 --> 00:17:15.200 align:middle line:90%
on a day-to-day basis.

00:17:15.200 --> 00:17:17.960 align:middle line:84%
And through our
addictive behaviors,

00:17:17.960 --> 00:17:22.760 align:middle line:84%
we seek the stimulation
that will deny that pain,

00:17:22.760 --> 00:17:24.599 align:middle line:84%
so we don't have
to feel that pain,

00:17:24.599 --> 00:17:26.440 align:middle line:84%
and so we then
become blocked off

00:17:26.440 --> 00:17:30.990 align:middle line:84%
on both the light and the
love that will heal us

00:17:30.990 --> 00:17:33.830 align:middle line:84%
and will give us a sense
of happiness and well-being

00:17:33.830 --> 00:17:34.670 align:middle line:90%
in life.

00:17:34.670 --> 00:17:37.170 align:middle line:84%
I always say that,
there is pain in life,

00:17:37.170 --> 00:17:38.510 align:middle line:90%
but that misery is optional.

00:17:38.510 --> 00:17:43.040 align:middle line:84%
>> [LAUGHS] Yes, so it is how
