00:17:43.040 --> 00:17:44.020 align:middle line:90%
>> It is.

00:17:44.020 --> 00:17:45.020 align:middle line:90%
>> Uh-huh.

00:17:45.020 --> 00:17:48.020 align:middle line:84%
