totally in touch with life

00:20:29.090 --> 00:20:34.610 align:middle line:84%
and have an open heart and how
through our painful experiences

00:20:34.610 --> 00:20:39.620 align:middle line:84%
with our parents in childhood,
start to lose part of ourselves

00:20:39.620 --> 00:20:43.310 align:middle line:84%
and then grow up and
attract those same types

00:20:43.310 --> 00:20:46.280 align:middle line:84%
of parental figures
into our lives

00:20:46.280 --> 00:20:51.050 align:middle line:84%
until we reach a point in
life where we're in denial,

00:20:51.050 --> 00:20:54.290 align:middle line:84%
and that's when tragedy and
crisis comes into our lives.

00:20:54.290 --> 00:20:56.210 align:middle line:84%
>> And we have set
up a pattern then.

00:20:56.210 --> 00:21:00.320 align:middle line:84%
>> Exactly, and living
life based on fear instead

00:21:00.320 --> 00:21:03.170 align:middle line:84%
of the trust and love that
will move us forward in life.

00:21:03.170 --> 00:21:05.985 align:middle line:84%
>> And the good news is we
can move forward in life.

00:21:05.985 --> 00:21:06.785 align:middle line:90%
[CHUCKLES]

